    "title": "Choosing an API for Implementing Apple Pay on Your Website"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Safari supports two APIs for implementing payment requests: ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/apple_pay_on_the_web/apple_pay_js_api",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ", and the W3C ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/apple_pay_on_the_web/payment_request_api",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ". Both APIs present the same Apple Pay payment sheet on Safari, and offer nearly the same user experience. ",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To help you decide which API to implement, or whether to implement both, first determine which features your solution requires, and choose the API that matches your needs.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "2957528",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Features of Apple Pay JS API",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Use ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/apple_pay_on_the_web/apple_pay_js_api",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " if you depend on any of its unique features:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "Granular error handling.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "strong"
            },
            {
              "text": " You can provide robust error handling: ",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Customizable error messages and field indications create a better user experience. See ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/apple_pay_on_the_web/applepayerror",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " for more information.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "You can report errors the user can correct, even after the user authorizes payment.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "You can retry if an error occurs after the user authorizes payment. With ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/apple_pay_on_the_web/payment_request_api",
                      "isActive": false,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", the user must restart their transaction.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "Integration for store cards and cobranded debit/credit cards. ",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "strong"
            },
            {
              "text": "When customers with affiliated cards visit your website, you can provide these additional benefits:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Apple Pay can automatically select the affiliated card instead of the customer's default card.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "You can adjust prices or other terms of a sale for customers using your affiliated card. For example, you might provide free shipping when customers use your cobranded VISA credit card.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "Phonetic names.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "strong"
            },
            {
              "text": " You can request a phonetic name in ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/apple_pay_on_the_web/apple_pay_js_api",
              "isActive": false,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " only.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "2957526",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Features of Payment Request API",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Use ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/apple_pay_on_the_web/payment_request_api",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " for these benefits:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "inlineContent": [
                        {
                          "text": "Cross-browser solution. ",
                          "type": "text"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type": "strong"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Payment Request API-based code can support a variety platforms and browsers. Apple Pay is available on Safari; other payment methods are available on other browsers and platforms. ",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "inlineContent": [
                        {
                          "text": "W3C standard candidate API.  ",
                          "type": "text"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type": "strong"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "The Payment Request API is defined by the ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "link-2961200",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". ",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "2957527",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Choose an API to Support Your Customers",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To better reach your customers, choose an API that works on their devices, as follows:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "inlineContent": [
                        {
                          "text": "Apple Pay JS API:",
                          "type": "text"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type": "strong"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " Supported in iOS 10 and later, and macOS 10.12 and later.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "inlineContent": [
                        {
                          "text": "Payment Request API:",
                          "type": "text"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type": "strong"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " Supported in iOS 11.3 and later, and Safari 11.1 on macOS 10.12 and later.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "When implementing ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/apple_pay_on_the_web/payment_request_api",
              "isActive": false,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ", consider also implementing ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/apple_pay_on_the_web/apple_pay_js_api",
              "isActive": false,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " as a fallback for customers whose devices run an older operating system version.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "2957529",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Requirements for Both APIs",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The same first steps, configurations, and guidelines for using Apple Pay on the web apply regardless of which API you choose to implement.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "For more information, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/apple_pay_on_the_web#2930228",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ",  ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/apple_pay_on_the_web#2930449",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ", and for design guidance see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "link-2957564",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
